OL,3,C'He stole my childhood': Survivors on
OL,4,Crelease of paedophile from jail
OL,6,FSurvivors of one of Northern Ireland's
OL,7,Fmost notorious paedophiles have hit
OL,8,Fout at the decision to release him.
OL,10,F58-year-old Billy Adams committed
OL,11,Fhorrific sex crimes against children
OL,12,Fin Northern Ireland, the Republic of
OL,13,FIreland and England.
OL,15,FHe is no longer deemed a danger
OL,16,Fdespite being refused parole seven
OL,17,Ftimes.
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Justice told UTV that
OL,20,Fhe will be recalled to prison if he
OL,21,Fbreaks strict licence conditions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
