OL,3,C'He stole my childhood': Survivors on
OL,4,Crelease of paedophile from jail
OL,6,FA spokesperson explained decisions are
OL,7,Fsolely based on risk and protection of
OL,8,Fthe public is key.
OL,10,FUTV understands survivors were told he
OL,11,Fwill be able to be monitored safely in
OL,12,Fthe community.
